content.description:
This has two problems: Little Brown Jug Haul, V0, and Little Brown Jug Wall, V1.

The wall faces west. The route on the left is V0 and this one is immediately right.

Eds. this was originally one submission for two problems.  It was split up during the reorganization.
content.protection: Crash pad and spotter are helpful.
content.location: This nice warm-up is about 30-40' west of The Corporate View Block on the upper tier of The North Rim of the Upper Canyon.
